      "name": "Sticky Note"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "##  AI Agent\n**- Processes user message\n- Uses:\n  • Chat Model (Google Gemini)\n  • Memory (Simple Memory for context)\n  • Tools:\n      - Products (Google Sheet)\n      - FAQs (Google Sheet)\n\n- Input:\n  {{ $json[\"text\"] || $json[\"message\"] }}\n\n- Output:\n  Smart reply based on products + FAQs\n\n---\n\nSTEP 3: Send Message\n- Sends response back to user on WhatsApp\n- Uses WhatsApp Cloud API\n- Requires:\n  • Phone Number ID\n  • Access Token\n  • Correct recipient number\n\n---\n\n⚠️ IMPORTANT CHECKS\n\n1. Webhook must be LIVE\n   → Use Production URL (NOT test URL)\n\n2. Workflow must be ACTIVE\n   → Otherwise Meta cannot verify\n\n3. Verify Token must MATCH\n   → Same in Meta & n8n\n\n4. ngrok must be RUNNING\n   → URL should not change\n\n5. Meta App does NOT need to be published (for testing)\n   → Just use test number\n\n---\n\n🚨 COMMON ERRORS\n\n❌ \"Callback URL couldn't be validated\"\n→ Webhook not active OR wrong URL\n\n❌ \"Bad request\"\n→ Wrong credentials OR token mismatch\n\n❌ \"Node unexecuted\"\n→ Nodes not connected properly\n\n---",
        "height": 848,
        "width": 864
      },
